org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.kafka.internals

类 KafkaTopicPartitionStateWithPunctuatedWatermarks<T,KPH>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.kafka.internals.KafkaTopicPartitionState<KPH>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.kafka.internals.KafkaTopicPartitionStateWithPunctuatedWatermarks<T,KPH>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of records handled by the watermark generator
    KPH - The type of the Kafka partition descriptor, which varies across Kafka versions

    public final class KafkaTopicPartitionStateWithPunctuatedWatermarks<T,KPH>
extends KafkaTopicPartitionState<KPH>
    A special version of the per-kafka-partition-state that additionally holds a periodic watermark generator (and timestamp extractor) per partition.

    This class is not thread safe, but it gives volatile access to the current partition watermark (getCurrentPartitionWatermark()).
